title: [Whistler's Pass]
description: A dull night sky gazes down with little emotion, its blank complexion scarred slightly by the tattered vestiges of forlorn clouds and the faint glimmer of tiny stars.  A chill wind dances about the pass, its force, from a bare whisper to a harsh gust, ever-changing.
